Class RawMotorCommand

java.lang.Object
  se.nicklasgavelin.sphero.command.CommandMessage
      se.nicklasgavelin.sphero.command.RawMotorCommand

public class RawMotorCommand
extends CommandMessage

Command to steer the direction and speed of the internal motors of the Sphero. NOTICE: Sending this command will result in some future commands to fail to execute on the Sphero for some reason. Has something to do with the logic on the Sphero

Author:
Nicklas Gavelin, nicklas.gavelin@gmail.com, Lule√• University of Technology
